channel.title: Help me fast please
channel.description: Ok, so i downloaded a source/client called casinoscape v1 is client second reality is source. When i load up the server to turn it on, and it says its online, port 5555. I load up client, try to login, it says error conencting to server. Please help. I tried looking for 127.0.0.1 in client.java and i tried lookin for 5555 port, cant find anything, im a begginer coder, im into PI's people said its easiest to learn, so please help, and if u dont know, post a link to download a good PI client/source or to a thread with a download? Thanks!
